\\\"datetime\\\": 1772510880, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Facing backlash, OpenAI’s Sam Altman says he made a ‘sloppy’ mistake in Pentagon deal\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580329, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"The OpenAI CEO admits he came off as “opportunistic” in how he announced the company’s new government deal and says he will amend the language to emphasize restrictions\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/facing-backlash-openais-sam-altman-says-he-made-a-sloppy-mistake-in-pentagon-deal-cf8f3ad9\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772504580, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"MongoDB’s stock sinks after earnings, signaling more tough times for the software sector\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580321, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"A “planned” transition involving the exits of two sales leaders is also rattling investors.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/mongodbs-stock-sinks-after-earnings-signaling-more-tough-times-for-the-software-sector-5dd37daa\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772501280, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"SoFi’s stock rises as CEO Anthony Noto reacts to recent selloff with a $1 million purchase\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580315, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Noto, who already owns a SoFi stake worth about $215 million on paper, has been known to buy the dip before.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/sofis-stock-rises-as-ceo-anthony-noto-reacts-to-recent-selloff-with-a-1-million-purchase-d03ba5b6\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772496001, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Jim Cramer explains why the stock market shrugged off fears over the Iran war and bad headlines\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580383, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/107109967-1661524568032-NUP_198430_00186r.jpg?v=1690933351&w=1920&h=1080\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"CNBC\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"The Middle East no longer carries the same economic weight it once did, CNBC Jim Cramer said on \\\\\\\"Mad Money\\\\\\\" on Monday.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/02/jim-cramer-why-stock-market-shrugged-off-iran-bad-headlines.html\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772492460, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"How this under-the-radar U.S. natural-gas exporter could capitalize on a potential shortage in Europe\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580299, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"The U.S. is the world’s largest exporter of liquefied natural gas, and one relatively obscure U.S. company seems ready to reap the benefits of a surge in global natural-gas prices following the U.S. and Israel’s attacks on Iran and the widening conflict in the Middle East.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/how-this-under-the-radar-u-s-natural-gas-exporter-could-capitalize-on-a-potential-shortage-in-europe-c6938bab\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772490900, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"The smartest money moves to make as the Iran conflict rattles markets\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580298, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"You may have opportunities to optimize for short-term volatility, financial planners told MarketWatch.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/the-smartest-money-moves-to-make-as-the-iran-conflict-rattles-markets-d8e57ef3\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772488020, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"As global markets tanked over Iran, U.S. stocks were mostly unscathed. Here’s why.\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580291, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"There is an old saying in markets: Buy when the bullets (or bombs or missiles) fly.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/as-global-markets-tanked-over-iran-u-s-stocks-were-mostly-unscathed-heres-why-92dc87c5\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772487960, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Gold just passed its stress test — what happens next will tell investors if they’re right\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580292, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Gold did exactly what it was supposed to after the Iran strike. Is the spike temporary or a new era for the safe-haven trade?\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/gold-just-passed-its-stress-test-what-happens-next-will-tell-investors-if-theyre-right-35de6d2f\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772487600, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Iran conflict unlikely to hurt U.S. economy or boost inflation — but the Fed won’t be quick to cut rates\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580272, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"The U.S. attack on Iran won’t boost U.S. inflation or harm the economy in a major way, analysts say, unless in the unlikely case that the conflict drags on for months and sharply raises the price of oil.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/iran-conflict-unlikely-to-hurt-u-s-economy-or-boost-inflation-but-the-fed-wont-be-quick-to-cut-rates-6e7d315a\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772487180, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Trump’s war on Iran could make many things more expensive, despite his affordability promises\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580273, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"How do you campaign on “affordability” if you just pushed up prices?\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/trumps-war-on-iran-could-make-many-things-more-expensive-despite-his-affordability-promises-66060ea4\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772484180, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Iran conflict hits a market that’s more overvalued than during the 1973 oil shock\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580262, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Arab–Israeli war in 1973 and the oil embargo that followed shows that stocks don’t always rebound quickly.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/iran-conflict-hits-a-market-thats-more-overvalued-than-during-the-1973-oil-shock-f9035d9d\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772481480, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Here is the ‘worst-case scenario’ for oil and the Strait of Hormuz\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580256, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Oil climbed to its highest price since June on Monday, as conflict in the Middle East brings with it an inherent risk to the world’s available crude supplies.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/here-is-the-worst-case-scenario-for-oil-and-the-strait-of-hormuz-d1aada30\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772480400, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Why CrowdStrike’s stock just got an upgrade ahead of earnings\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580251, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"An analyst sees minimal risk to the company’s guidance and thinks shares have been overly punished by a broad selloff in the software sector.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/why-crowdstrikes-stock-just-got-an-upgrade-ahead-of-earnings-1a7450be\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772480195, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"We're upgrading our rating on Nvidia shares. Here's why\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580261, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108248994-1767729949197-gettyimages-2254367461-AFP_89UC72B.jpeg?v=1772476350&w=1920&h=1080\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"CNBC\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"The market punished the stock after a strong earnings report with an even strong guide.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/02/jim-cramers-investing-club-upgrades-nvidia-nvda-here-is-why.html\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772479165, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Apple's new budget version of its iPhone 17 is a positive for investors\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580252, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108156700-1749492383905-gettyimages-2219347508-_75a6261_xqpv981e.jpeg?v=1756303854&w=1920&h=1080\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"CNBC\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Every weekday, the Investing Club releases the Homestretch, an actionable afternoon update just in time for the last hour of trading.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https:/