image/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"The satellite-communications company is essentially a hedge fund with a SpaceX stake, in the view of MoffettNathanson analysts.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/echostars-business-deemed-irrelevant-as-investors-focus-on-future-spacex-stake-5a89c0c7\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772474760, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Most Americans are oblivious to the fact their Social Security checks could be slashed 20% in as soon as 6 years\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580231, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"Would an education campaign help workers or cause panic?\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.marketwatch.com/story/most-americans-are-oblivious-to-the-fact-their-social-security-checks-could-be-slashed-20-in-as-soon-as-6-years-aded9dd0\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772474131, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Trump says the U.S. is 'richer and stronger than ever'—why some Americans don't feel it\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580232, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://image.cnbcfm.com/api/v1/image/108269704-1771998597707-gettyimages-2262903854-AFP_98UU9KZ.jpeg?v=1771998620&w=1920&h=1080\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"CNBC\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"President Donald Trump touted economic wins during his State of the Union address. But Americans and economists say affordability is still a major issue.\\\", \\\"url\\\": \\\"https://www.cnbc.com/2026/03/02/trump-touts-affordability-some-americans-still-feel-crisis.html\\\"}, {\\\"category\\\": \\\"top news\\\", \\\"datetime\\\": 1772473320, \\\"headline\\\": \\\"Apple launches new iPhone and iPad Air as it gears up for a major AI push\\\", \\\"id\\\": 7580218, \\\"image\\\": \\\"https://static2.finnhub.io/file/publicdatany/finnhubimage/market_watch_logo.png\\\", \\\"related\\\": \\\"\\\", \\\"source\\\": \\\"MarketWatch\\\", \\\"summary\\\": \\\"The c\",\n  \"content_schema\": {\n    \"$schema\": \"http://json-schema.org/schema#\",\n    \"type\": \"array\",\n    \"items\": {\n      \"type\": \"object\",\n      \"properties\": {\n        \"category\": {\n          \"type\": \"string\"\n        },\n        \"datetime\": {\n          \"type\": \"integer\"\n        },\n        \"headline\": {\n          \"type\": \"string\"\n        },\n        \"id\": {\n          \"type\": \"integer\"\n        },\n        \"image\": {\n          \"type\": \"string\"\n        },\n        \"related\": {\n          \"type\": \"string\"\n        },\n        \"source\": {\n          \"type\": \"string\"\n        },\n        \"summary\": {\n          \"type\": \"string\"\n        },\n        \"url\": {\n          \"type\": \"string\"\n        }\n      },\n      \"required\": [\n        \"category\",\n        \"datetime\",\n        \"headline\",\n        \"id\",\n        \"image\",\n        \"related\",\n        \"source\",\n        \"summary\",\n        \"url\"\n      ]\n    }\n  }\n}","cwd":"/Users/lynch/.openclaw/workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1772539841143}}
{"type":"message","id":"e1ad9e59","parentId":"058703e4","timestamp":"2026-03-03T12:11:07.445Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The Finnhub news endpoint doesn't have a \"hotness\" field either. It has category, datetime, headline, id, image, related, source, summary, url - no sentiment or hotness score.\n\nLet me think about this differently. The user asked for \"热度≥80\" (hotness ≥80). Looking at the available data:\n\n1. **AlphaVantage news sentiment**: Has `overall_sentiment_score` which ranges roughly from -0.5 to +0.5, and `overall_sentiment_label` (Bearish, Somewhat-Bearish, Neutral, Somewhat_Bullish, Bullish). If we map this to 0-100:\n   - Bearish (-0.5) → 0\n   - Somewhat-Bearish (-0.25) → 25\n   - Neutral (0) → 50\n   - Somewhat-Bullish (0.25) → 75\n   - Bullish (0.5) → 100\n\nSo \"热度≥80\" would be roughly `overall_sentiment_score` >= 0.3.\n\n2. **Finnhub news**: Has no sentiment/hotness field at all.\n\nSince the user specifically asked for Finnhub but Finnhub doesn't have a hotness metric, I should explain this limitation and provide what's available. However, looking at the AlphaVantage data I already retrieved, I can filter for high-sentiment news (score >= 0.3 which would be like \"hotness\" >= 80).\n\nLet me provide the user with the information I found - Finnhub doesn't have a \"hotness\" metric, but I can offer the AlphaVantage sentiment data as an alternative, or explain that I can only provide general Finnhub news without hotness filtering.\n\nActually, wait - I should be careful here. The user might be referring to a specific Finnhub feature I'm not aware of. \n\nI need to acknowledge that Finnhub doesn't provide a hotness metric in its news data, so I can't directly filter for that threshold. The sentiment scores from AlphaVantage would be the closest alternative if I map them to a 0-100 scale.","thinkingSignature":"84d99404f09c77fb1883613f2dd2573097a9510f2fe1bd2e13a7e63c891e6f71"},{"type":"text","text":"我检查了Finnhub的新闻API，发现它**没有\"热度\"（hotness）字段**。Finnhub的市场新闻返回的是：category、datetime、headline、source、summary等，但没有情感评分或热度指数。\n\n**可用的替代方案：**\n\n**AlphaVantage新闻情感数据**包含`overall_sentiment_score`（-0.5到+0.5范围），可以转换为0-100的热度标度：\n\n| 情感标签 | 分数 | 热度(0-100) |\n|---------|------|-------------|\n| Bearish | -0.5 | 0 |\n| Somewhat-Bearish | -0.25 | 25 |\n| Neutral | 0 | 50 |\n| Somewhat-Bullish | +0.25 | 75 |\n| Bullish | +0.5 | 100 |\n\n根据已获取的AlphaVantage数据，**热度≥80的新闻**（sentiment_score ≥ 0.3）包括：\n\n1. **Fortinet's Fairtree Asset Management Boosts Stake by 185%** - Bullish (0.42)\n2. **Allison Transmission Holdings** - Somewhat-Bullish (0.34)\n3. **GE Vernova Inc.** - Somewhat-Bullish (0.34)\n4. **Norfolk Southern Corporation** - Somewhat-Bullish (0.31)\n\n---\n\n**请问您希望：**\n1. 发送上述高热度新闻给您？\n2. 还是您有其他方式定义\"热度\"指标？\n\n目前QVeris可用的Finnhub功能仅为新闻检索，没有热度/情感评分。"}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.5","usage":{"input":29063,"output":780,"cacheRead":13984,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43827,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1772539841145}}
